description:
Part 28 of 31. Rain makes plants grow, and grow, and grow! The Bible says, He [God] shall come to us as the rain Hosea 6:3. Rain is also a symbol of the Holy Spirit. In this powerful new message, Steve Wohlberg explains how the Holy Spirit can help us grow, and grow, and grow closer to God in this ungodly world.  https://youtu.be/2y2wW7Zc3Go
